{
  "stem": "22734.5",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Were we-- we were, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] at that point in time, in 1943, the rails went through into Theresien.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the cattle wagons were standing there, and there was a big board from the-- from the road, if you will, from wherever, into the cattle wagons, because the cattle wagons are-- the openings are high.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And when the wagon was full, so they sealed it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They locked it, and they-- locked it up.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then, until the whole train was done, which took about three hours, four hours, I have-- it took a long time.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "A whole day, I think.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Then we left.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was dark.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the engines, to this day, I can't hear that the-- the locomotive makes a very-- made a very special sound, it's an Auschwitz sound.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I can't reproduce it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It's sort of a mourning sound that they made.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And in that wagon, there were about 100 people and one pail for bodily needs, and one pail with water, which was gone in no time, because the train shook and the water spilled.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And there was a little window, high up, which was behind bars, a small window, but not-- not open.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But there was a window.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And once the train stopped and somebody climbed over somebody's shoulders and looked out, and we realized that we were going through [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the eastern part of the protectorate.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It was a city where there were many coal mines.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We were going east, that was obvious.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We knew where we were.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And then-- I don't know how long the journey took.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "There were people and there was crying.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And we were holding on to each other.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And people finally relieved themselves where they were because they couldn't help it.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
